==== Recruitment Challenges

    - Early-stage ME/CFS patients may not yet have diagnosis; outreach to primary care needed
    - Patients may be reluctant to be randomized to standard care; detailed informed consent about clinical equipoise
    - 12-month symptom onset window limits eligible population
*Mitigation*
    - Partnership with post-COVID clinics (rapid identification of post-infectious cases)
    - Provider education campaign
    - Clear communication that standard care is current best practice, not inferior care

